Protocol versions supported: V1..V6 (the SDK targets V5 for the MVP)

V5+ ships protocol.proto only — discovery is JSON-only via
endpoint_manifest_schema.json. There is no discovery.proto in V5.

Files vendored as-is, no modifications:
  dev/restate/service/protocol.proto       (671 lines)
  endpoint_manifest_schema.json
  service-invocation-protocol.md           (reference spec)

Refresh procedure:
  git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/restatedev/sdk-shared-core /tmp/ssc
  cp /tmp/ssc/service-protocol/dev/restate/service/protocol.proto  ./dev/restate/service/
  cp /tmp/ssc/service-protocol/endpoint_manifest_schema.json       .
  cp /tmp/ssc/service-protocol/service-invocation-protocol.md      .

Regenerate Elixir modules (requires `protoc` and the `protoc-gen-elixir`
escript from `mix escript.install hex protobuf`). Run from repo root:

  rm -rf apps/restate_protocol/lib/restate/protocol/generated
  mkdir -p apps/restate_protocol/lib/restate/protocol/generated
  protoc \
    --plugin=protoc-gen-elixir=$HOME/.mix/escripts/protoc-gen-elixir \
    --elixir_out=apps/restate_protocol/lib/restate/protocol/generated \
    --proto_path=apps/restate_protocol/proto \
    apps/restate_protocol/proto/dev/restate/service/protocol.proto

Generated modules are namespaced `Dev.Restate.Service.Protocol.*` (matches
the proto package). Use `alias Dev.Restate.Service.Protocol, as: Pb` in
calling code.
